# deploy2.out - Card Shopper (improve pass, terminal-enabled)

Finish-and-polish deploy. This run HAS a terminal, so the terminal follow-ups the
first run flagged are now done for real. Deploy = git push (fire-and-trust). Live
site/API are unreachable from this Zscaler environment, so no live polling was done
or claimed.

## Build (real, not static)

- `npm run build` in michaelwegter.com: PASS. vite v6.4.2, 46 modules transformed,
